short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Historic events, famous birthdays and holidays on your new tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension lists historic events, birthdays and holidays for every day of the year. Discover the historic events that have taken place throughout history from your new browser tab. Also included is a web search powered by Yahoo! and displays the time and day displayed in the right corner.
